    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 10px;">
      <p style="margin: 0;">
        Dear Insider,
<br><br>
As we form new ways to connect with the Coach community, we wanted to let you know that the Coach Insider program will end on November 6, 2025.
<br><br>
We remain committed to delivering exceptional customer service both in-store and online, offering distinctive shopping experiences and providing the high-quality products you know and love.
<br><br>
While this chapter is coming to a close, know that you will always be a valued part of the Coach community. No action is required on your part. Here are the details about this change:
<br><br>
      </p>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px 10px 10px 10px; font-weight: bold;">
      <b>Here’s what’s staying:</b>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px;"><ul>
      <li>You can still <a href="https://click.c.coach.com/?qs=8c6e4ec626deef31df44818d041155f9e61a974aa5a732515a8402680766cfd3483fa5b1b27f8cfb67c66ea249455d8b98a28bc55c1d9525f8c905e2eefb62f7" style="text-decoration: underline;">log in</a> to your Coach account to view your purchase history, manage wishlists, enjoy a faster checkout and redeem (Re)Loved Exchange credits.</li></ul>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px;"><ul>
      <li>If you have existing (Re)Loved Exchange credits, they’ll remain active for one year from the date issued, just as always. You can redeem them online by logging in to your account or in store by sharing your account email with a sales associate.</li></ul></td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px;"><ul>
      <li>The (Re)Loved Exchange program is here to stay—so you can continue to exchange used Coach bags for store credit. Learn more about (Re)Loved Exchange <a href="https://click.c.coach.com/?qs=8c6e4ec626deef31042ab14badbce899608d3a3e2f74aff2a4b7daed2f6ab8280e0fc9841843e6dd6a573f4c1d76feac168eae560a4a9dd364133683d59b347f" style="text-decoration: underline;">here</a>.
      </li></ul>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px;"><ul>
      <li>You can continue to enjoy the convenience of Easy Returns, now with even more flexibility. Starting today, all customers can return Coach and Coach Outlet items at any Coach or Coach Outlet store—no matter where they were purchased—as long as the items meet the terms of our return policy. </li></ul>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="520" style="max-width: 520px;" align="center">
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 10px 10px 10px 10px; font-weight: bold;">
      <b>Here’s what’s changing:</b>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px;"><ul>
      <li>If you have unused Free Customization rewards (up to $125), be sure to redeem them by January 5, 2026. (Please note: free customization is only available for eligible Coach products; Coach Outlet products are excluded.)</li></ul>
    </td>
  </tr>
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 0px;"><ul>
      <li>Free shipping on all Coach and Coach Outlet orders will be available to existing Insiders until January 5, 2026. After that date, it will be available on orders of $75+.</li></ul>
    </td>
  </tr>
</table>
<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" width="520" style="max-width: 520px;" align="center">
  <tr>
    <td align="left" class="nav-content" style="font-family: sans-serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.2; padding: 10px 10px 10px 10px;">
      If you wish to delete your Coach Insider account, you can email us at <a href="mailto:coachinsider@coach.com" style="text-decoration: underline;">coachinsider@coach.com</a>. Please note that this will permanently delete your online Coach account and information associated with it.
<br><br>
Additionally, if you’d like all your personal data—including your easy access to past orders—to be deleted, please email <a href="mailto:privacy@tapestry.com" style="text-decoration: underline;">privacy@tapestry.com</a>. You may also unsubscribe from our marketing emails <a href="https://click.c.coach.com/?qs=8c6e4ec626deef316ab1b5c16d8e4788ab2321cde4d8f139cff99f45193fa0917bb21d61a454cae3db18e32e3191ba37ee77f520e764b307ea76d37ef2c64d11" style="text-decoration: underline;">here</a>. Please review our <a href="https://click.c.coach.com/?qs=8c6e4ec626deef31478a001f9a057bf2e3841f9b335384b5b8a9cf73ee6bf2600d0d67ed1f31b997b22b4c6fd458cd7e74f930b8ec9479eabf924c7371377035" style="text-decoration: underline;">privacy policy</a> for more details.
<br><br>
      <b>Let’s stay connected.</b><br>
Sign up for emails to get the scoop on new arrivals, exclusive offers and more. <br><a href="https://click.c.coach.com/?qs=8c6e4ec626deef316ab1b5c16d8e4788ab2321cde4d8f139cff99f45193fa0917bb21d61a454cae3db18e32e3191ba37ee77f520e764b307ea76d37ef2c64d11" style="text-decoration: underline;">Sign Up Now</a>
<br><br>
Thank you for being a part of our community. We’re excited for what’s ahead—and we’re so glad you’re with us.
<br><br>
All our best,<br>
Your friends at Coach
<br><br>
